textRun.content: That the ASCSU distribute this resolution to: \n

Academic Senate for the California Community Colleges  \n
Academic Senate of the University of California  \n
California Community Colleges\u2019 Board of Governors  \n
University of California Board of Regents  \n
Legislative Leadership, [indicate which leadership members \u2013 speaker pro temp? caucus whip? Chair of a particular committee?] \n
For additional Legislative distribution a listing of California State Assembly Committees can be found here: http://assembly.ca.gov/committees,  \n
For additional Legislative distribution a listing of California Senate committees can be found here: http://senate.ca.gov/committees\n
Delete unnecessary recipients and add additional recipients if warranted
